NB. Miscellaneous

morim=: >./"1 @: | @: +.  NB. monad: max of real and imaginary parts' modules, max(|Re(y)|,|Im(y)|)
sgn=: (*!.0)`1:@.(0&=)    NB. monad: (if y<0 then -1 else 1 endif), for reals equiv. to: (0&(<:->))
sgnr=: sgn @ (9 & o.)     NB. monad: sgn(Re(y))

