NB. lartgc1
NB. algorithm 3 for case 1: f≠0, g≠0, neither f nor g too big
NB. or small, minimal work
NB. Note: (% sgnr) = (* sgnr)

lartgc1=: 3 : 0
  'f2 g2'=. soris 'f g'=. y
  d1=. (sgnr f) % %: f2 * fg2=. f2 + g2
  fd1=. f * d1
  (f2 * d1) , (fd1 * + g) , (fd1 * fg2)
)

